Rating: 4.0 -------------------------------------------------- === Purchase Information === Product Title: Makeup Brush Cleaning Mat Review Date: 2016/08/20 Store: KEDSUM Average Rating: 4.5 Product Details: {'Brand': 'KEDSUM', 'Skin Type': 'All', 'Item Form': 'Wand', 'Number of Pieces': '3', 'Age Range (Description)': 'Adult', 'Ferrule Material': 'Aluminum', 'Item Weight': '0.29 Pounds'} Review Text: Nice makeup cleaning mat set, designed to keep your makeup brushes clean and healthy for your face. Old makeup on your makeup brushes harbor bacteria and can reap havac on your face. Washing my makeup brushes has been a chore and gets very messy at times. This set of makeup brush cleaner does a good job cleaning my brushes. The set comes with three pieces... The large mat, has suction cups on the bottom to help keep it secured while you clean your brushes. Each section of the mat targets different types of brushes. The small heart shaped brush cleaner had a pocket to hold mat to deep scub brushes, and a makeup blender. The mats are easy to use and does a good job of giving my brushes a good cleaning. My brushes has natural hairs and it is hard to get deep down in the brissels to get all the makeup out. The mat helps and eliminates the need for me to use my hands to scrub. This mat got my brushes really clean. The makeup blender works good as well. Using this set you will not be disappointed. I am happy with this product, nothing like clean brushes.

I received the product for free in return for my unbiased opinion. The views expressed in this review at my own unbiased honest opinion of this product and was not compensated in any for it.
